<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="400">2.2. How are variations created?</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can either form variations by creating different combinations of <a href="/en/item/settings/units">unit and quantity</a> or by using <a href="/en/item/settings/attributes">attributes</a>.</p>
</div>
<table id="table-creating-variations" class="tableblock frame-all grid-all stretch">
