<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Variations differ from each other in terms of quantity and unit, e.g.:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>Soap: 100ml, 250ml, 500ml</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div></div></td>
