<li>
<p>Throw pillow: Colour (red, black, grey) = 1 attribute</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>T-shirt: Colour (green, blue), size (S, M, L, XL) = 2 attributes</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Shoes: Colour (black, brown), size (5, 6, 7), width (narrow, normal) = 3 attributes</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div></div></td>
